metadata.name: Fossil Love
metadata.description:
A forgotten love, marked in the rocks by the centuries passing by, Fossil Love will never change, it will remain eternal. 
Cities may decay, the palaces will collapse in the abyss of time like ruins of an ancient civilization, Fossil love will not. 
It is that natural sign of a passage, of a broken heart, of a soul that yearns for the truth in its being Lost at Sea.
